# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   It makes the environments reproducible.
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, if you're building a library, you should not check in a lockfile.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock should be in version control.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock should be in version control.
# pdm.lock

